The Dodoma Regional Commissioner, Dr. Bilinith Mahenge has instructed Tanzania National Roads Agency (TANROADS) Dodoma RegionÂ Acting Manager, Salome Kabunda not to pay any money to the Musons Engineers and Contractor, until they repair a part of bending down Chinyasungwi Bridge. Dr. Mahenge issued the order during his official tour in Mpwapwa district to supervise different projects in the area after a heavy downpour. Dr. Mahenge noted that the area must be repaired to facilitate flow of traffic and people, adding that such mistakes should never be repeated.